O(n)log(n) to build the maxHeap, and O(k)log(n) to eat Candies.
 
 Arrays.sort won't work since it will cause O(k *n * log(n)), because:
1 ≤ N ≤ 10,000
1 ≤ k ≤ 10,000
the time will exceed 1e8.

Time: O(N + K * log(N)), space O(N) 
Reference: https://leetcode.com/discuss/interview-question/1184501/facebook-recruiting-portal-magical-candy-bags
